data.description: Low special assesments, brand new shingles! Well cared for home in a great neighborhood, this 4 bed/3 bath/3 stall offers great value! The kitchen has new flooring, backsplash and pantry. The deck looks over the large fenced in yard. The master suite has a large bedroom, walk-in closet and updated bathroom! New water heater is less than 1 year old. Call your favorite realtor for a showing today!
